            <title>[LU-4730] clean up &quot;lctl get_param&quot; and &quot;lctl set_param&quot; error reporting</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4730</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Clean up &quot;lctl get_param&quot; and &quot;lctl set_param&quot; code and error handling.  Remove deprecated full-path handling.  Deny &quot;parameters&quot; with embedded relative paths to avoid strange problems.  Return an error consistently if multiple parameters are set but the last one did not fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
